data.title: Rock 'n' Roll Graffiti
data.meta_description: The perfect oldies library. It's 1,229 of the most requested and audience-tested hits of the '50s and '60s. All original versions by the original artists, digitally re-mastered for superb sound without noise and scratches! Rock 'N' Roll Graffiti is on the air in over 600 markets worldwide.
